<<dialog "player">>Kitchen doesn't have great ventilation either.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>Nothing in this building works right. Part of the charm.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>That's one way to look at it.<</dialog>>
