<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>My friend keeps texting about some bar tonight.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>You going?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerWaitress1">>I'd have to shower, change, be a person. That's a lot of steps.<</dialog>>
